01:09:13.931 --> 01:09:17.931
We include metadata for what the available tools are.

01:09:17.931 --> 01:09:21.451
Then the assistant asks us to invoke the tool

01:09:21.451 --> 01:09:24.811
or asks Ellmer to invoke the tool and passes arguments.

01:09:24.811 --> 01:09:27.890
And then Ellmer or us, you know, we invoke the tool

01:09:27.890 --> 01:09:29.851
and then we return the output, okay?

