That is a really, I think,

01:17:10.530 --> 01:17:12.530
what people see as a really important tool

01:17:12.530 --> 01:17:14.331
for a lot of people to think about.

01:17:14.331 --> 01:17:16.331
And I think it's a really important tool

01:17:16.331 --> 01:17:18.371
for a lot of people to think about.

01:17:18.371 --> 01:17:20.371
And I think it's a really important tool

01:17:20.371 --> 01:17:22.410
for a lot of people to think about.

01:17:22.410 --> 01:17:25.290
I think what people see as a really important use case

01:17:25.290 --> 01:17:28.491
for these LLMs, like the ability to have

01:17:28.491 --> 01:17:30.931
the LLM drive software that was not intended

01:17:30.931 --> 01:17:33.610
to be driven by other software.

01:17:33.610 --> 01:17:34.451
Absolutely.

01:17:35.451 --> 01:17:38.410
